{"tid":1938634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（請大家幫手)大家仲記得被畜警射盲眼女記者嗎？","createTime":"2020-03-22T16:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T00:21:51.000Z","uid":32473,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"06071a33803d218dcc9d1cc97f1edcfe2e041f22","tid":1938634,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"佢需要全香港人既幫忙<br />\n私人起訴左畜警<br />\n但29/3/2020就係6個月deadline <br />\n因為警畜拒絕提供射佢個果隻狗既資料<br />\n所以如果有人知道 認到隻請你地幫幫手<br />\n制裁呢隻畜生<br />\n還記者一個公義<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/258109148210812/posts/500528913968833/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F258109148210812%2Fposts%2F500528913968833%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=ef09cbab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/258109148210812/posts/500528913968833/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【時限快到、刻不容緩、敬請廣傳】<br />\n<br />\n（Mayi山寨翻譯。如有錯漏，敬請見諒）<br />\n<br />\n//你還記得嗎？我們現在需要幫助這個女人、這個記者。<br />\n<br />\n我們需要射手的身份。即刻。<br />\n<br />\n誰射中Veby？<br />\n<br />\n印尼前線記者Veby Mega Indah於9月29日，被香港警察射中右眼致盲。<br />\n<br />\nVeby在香港的印尼語報紙Suara工作。<br />\n<br />\n她的案件已要私人起訴（注：因香港警察根本沒有當刑事case執法），但事件發生六個月後，所有私人起訴均被失效。<br />\n<br />\n她需要射手的身份。香港警方不斷拖延並拒絕透露射手的名字。<br />\n<br />\n她的截止日期是29.3.20<br />\n<br />\n第一張照片就是射手。<br />\n<br />\n他叫什麼名字？//"},{"pid":"dcaabd09b9c59980d2cc6990112fef9e8cbf3bc7","tid":1938634,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ErTCVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ErTCVS.png&h=227be43d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJfUnnA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJfUnnA.png&h=36df7aaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"409bd067aab2c597cb225dc204ca1f879cb5ca86","tid":1938634,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手